      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S TALKING (8) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from eight tries. In the money last time at this track (17.00) in a Restricted WIN H, finishing a 5.5 lengths third. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. STORM COMING (4) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Traralgon in a handy 24.40 beating Lucky Spin. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Should be in this for a long way. MAJOR ILLUSION (3) turned in a solid run last start over 350m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (19.78). Comes out of a solid form race last start. One of the main contenders. ASTON RENNES (7) has strong credentials at this circuit over this journey.",
